=============================================================================
CHATOPTIONS PROPERTY CHEAT SHEET
=============================================================================

new ChatOptions
{
    ConversationId = "user-123",              // Conversation tracking
    Instructions = "You are a helpful...",    // Per-request system prompt
    Temperature = 0.7,                        // 0 = deterministic, 1 = random
    MaxOutputTokens = 2048,                   // Max response length
    TopP = 0.9,                               // Nucleus sampling (0-1)
    TopK = 40,                                // Top-K tokens to consider
    FrequencyPenalty = 0.5,                   // Penalize repetition
    PresencePenalty = 0.5,                    // Penalize already-mentioned topics
    Tools = new List<AITool> { ... },         // Functions available to LLM
    ToolMode = ChatToolMode.Auto,             // Auto | Required | None
    AllowBackgroundResponses = false,         // Allow async background ops
    ResponseFormat = new ChatResponseFormatJson(), // Require JSON output
    // AdditionalProperties for provider-specific settings
}

=============================================================================
AITOOL/AIFUNCTION TYPE HIERARCHY
=============================================================================

AITool (Base)
├─ AIFunction (executable)
│  ├─ Implementation from AIFunctionFactory
│  └─ Properties: Name, Description, InvokeAsync()
├─ AIFunctionDeclaration (declaration only)
├─ ApprovalRequiredAIFunction (requires user approval)
└─ Provider-specific tools

=============================================================================
CHATMESSAGE ROLES
=============================================================================

ChatRole.System      → System prompt / instructions
ChatRole.User        → User input
ChatRole.Assistant   → LLM response
ChatRole.Tool        → Tool function result

=============================================================================
CONTENT TYPES IN CHATMESSAGE
=============================================================================

TextContent                    → Plain text
FunctionCallContent            → LLM requesting function call
FunctionResultContent          → Result from function execution
ToolCallContent                → Tool invocation request
ToolResultContent              → Tool result
ImageContent                   → Image data
UsageContent                   → Token usage information
UriContent                     → URI reference
DataContent                    → Binary data
ErrorContent                   → Error representation
ToolApprovalRequestContent     → Request for user approval

=============================================================================
AIFUNCTIONFACTORY METHOD SIGNATURES
=============================================================================

// From Delegate (simple function)
AIFunctionFactory.Create(
    Func<int, int> handler,
    string? name = null,
    AIFunctionFactoryOptions? options = null
)

// From Object Instance (reflection on public methods)
AIFunctionFactory.Create(
    object instance,
    AIFunctionFactoryOptions? options = null
)

// From Type (reflection on public static methods)
AIFunctionFactory.Create(
    Type type,
    AIFunctionFactoryOptions? options = null
)

